Friday August 23rd 2013 8:56 am -04:00,MORE is a pager ie. a program that when a text (in this case the help) is too long lets you view it one page at a time.Python always uses it for help but in your case it cant find it.Im quite certain that all versions of windows include MORE in the c:\Windows\System32 folder. But that folder might not be in your PATH system variable ie. where windows look for executables.You can look online to see how to change your path a good set of instructions I found is here http://geekswithblogs.net/renso/archive/2009/10/21/how-to-set-the-windows-path-in-windows-7.aspx, Resolved,0
